==Icelandic==

===Proper noun===
'''[[Þriðja]] [[Ríkið]]'''

# [[Germany]] under the [[Nazi]] regime, beginning in 1933 and ending in 1945. Literally "[[third]] [[empire]]" or "third [[realm]]/[[state]]".

===Usage notes===
''[[Ríkið]]'' in Icelandic is similar to the way [[Reich]] is used in German.

